verbose_text: Pre-treatment with ISDN reversed the decrease in miR-130b expression induced by HG stimulation (ISDN + HG group vs. HG group, 0.75 +/-0.11 vs. 0.39 +/-0.07; P < 0.05), but had no apparent effect on miR-130a expression (ISDN + HG group vs. HG group, 0.92 +/-0.13 vs. 0.93 +/-0.11; P> 0.05) (XREF_FIG).
